            <extref href="http://doddcenter.uconn.edu/asc/dodda2z/curatorinfo.cfm?curatorinfo=6">curator</extref> or ask at the reference desk.</p>
      </relatedmaterial>
      <arrangement encodinganalog="351$b" id="a5">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The collection has been reordered and divided into two series. Photographs were removed from original folders and placed in a separate folder created for photographs. Publications were also removed for cataloging.</p>
